# Rendering Guidelines
- Walk `entries` recursively:
  - strings → apply tag transforms
  - `entries/section` → render nested content
  - `list.items[]` → bullets
  - named blocks → `**Name.** content`
- Implement and test common tags first:
  - `{@spell}`, `{@item}`, `{@condition}`, `{@dice}`, `{@damage}`, `{@dc}`, `{@hit}`
- All inline links must point to `fiveet://entity/{kind}/{source}/{slug}`.
- Rendering must be deterministic (no random ordering).

